 @{fg shine}3@{fg text}. You may NOT disassemble or change the program(s) in anyway without
    written permission from the author of the program(s).

 @{fg shine}4@{fg text}. If you use the program you accept these rules and the defintion of
    FreeWare written above.

 Other restictions may be added by authors.

